c: 2
v: 128
t: "Mong`a rona! Re etse ba ithapalatsang thatong ea hau (Islamong), le tsoala ea rona u e etse sechaba se ithapalatsang thatong ea hau (Masolomane), u be u re bonts’e libaka tsa rona tsa thapelo, u be u retellehele ka ho rona. Ruri ke uena, uena feela ea retelehang-khafetsa, ea tletseng mohau"